Name: Goomanuvr
About the game: Goomanuvr is the silliest platformer about goo buddies tethered up trying to jump through life. We wanted to capture the hilariousness of working with a teammate (or you can fly solo) trying to get through various obstacles to get to your goal! Discover what it means to be a Goo. Limited or infinite mode. Simple to learn, hard to master Controller is REQUIRED!!!!!!!! Goo!
